high_descs: Turn around, move to the coffee machine, turn right, move to the stove.
Pick up the tomato on the counter, left of the stove.
Turn around, bring the tomato to the fridge.
Chill the tomato in the fridge.
Bring the chilled tomato to the microwave, right of the fridge.
Put the chilled tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the tomato closest to the edge of the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Cool the tomato in the fridge and then remove it.
Take a step to the right to face the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a tomato plus store it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go right to stand in front of the stove.
Pick the tomato up from the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge and close the door and then open the door and pick up the tomato and close the door again.
Move to the right and face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.
